Dear. Helen
H.E Mr. Molla,
Secretary General of GSO has announced the approval of the LVTR by the GSO
Council in its 20
th
Meeting held in Riyadh 5
th
Nov. 2014.
Technical Regulation has
been approved by the GSO Board of Directors in its 20th meeting (Riyadh, 5th
November 2014).
The enforcement will be in the 1st of June 2015 in an
experimental way, while the full enforcement will be in the 1st of July 2016.
GSO
